        {
            "title": "〈經濟部記者會〉中東戰火原油飆漲8成！中油每月狂燒百億淨值剩854億 爭取「三箭」紓困",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BxC1.LrhYOPoWqgdJzq.VA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/57fca70feeea8a66b125b20832d26684\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
